abstract: French and Spanish authorities report capture of Iratxe Sorzabal and David Pla, leaders of Basque separatist group ETA, in France; Jorge Fernandez Diaz, Spain's interior minister, expresses belief that capture of the pair will leave ETA leaderless and nonoperational.
lead_paragraph: Iratxe Sorzabal, 43, and David Pla, 40, were arrested in the small French town of Saint-Étienne-de-Baïgorry.

headline.print_headline: Europe; Spain: Basque Separatists Are Arrested
